Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=12}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:59.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is this a treasure map? - OG}Isso não é um mapa do tesouro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que aponta\Npra Vila Cocoyashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Treasure in Cocoyashi Village?! - OG}Tem tesouro na Vila Cocoyashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:10.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's my own personal map! - OG}{That's my personal map! - arch}Esse é meu mapa pessoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It has nothing to do with you at all! - OG}Isso não é da sua conta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:13.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh! - OG}{Hold it. - arch}Epa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong? You suddenly look so furious... - OG}{What's with the sudden evil eye? - arch}O que foi? Você parece chateada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What is this?! - OG}O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:25.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que diabos aconteceu aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:27.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's the work of Roronoa Zoro,\Nthe Pirate Hunter! - OG}Isso é obra do\NCaçador de Piratas Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But where were you, Hachi?! - OG}E onde você estava, Hachi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This could've been prevented\Nhad you been here! - OG}{We could have prevented this\Nhad you been here! - Gaijin}{This wouldn't have happened\Nhad you been here! - arch: Don't think "prevent" needs to be kept here, and it sounds really weird.}Isso não teria acontecido\Nse você estivesse aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Of course, we could've!\NHad I only been here! - OG}{Of course it wouldn't have!\NHad I only been here! - arch}Claro que não!\NSe ao menos eu estivesse aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é imperdoável!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:44.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Meaning you don't know where\NZoro disappeared to? - OG}{So, you don't know where\NZoro disappeared to? - arch}Então você não saberia pra onde\No Zoro desapareceu, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:50.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, all I saw was one\Nslightly suspicious swordsman, - OG}Bom, tudo que vi foi\Num espadachim peculiar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,que eu nunca tinha visto antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:57.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Era ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You did see him, you idiot! - OG}Então você viu ele, seu idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So, where did Zoro go?! - OG}Pra onde o Zoro foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:08.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He wanted to see Arlong-[/i1]san[/i0], so I just took him to Cocoyashi Village! - OG}{\q2}Ele queria ver o Capitão Arlong,\Nentão levei ele pra Vila Cocoyashi agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:14.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Meaning there's no reason\Nto rush out in a hurry. - OG}{Meaning there's no reason to rush out in a hurry and find him. - Gaijin}Ou seja, não tem por que\Nsair correndo atrás dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:18.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele também está me procurando.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:22.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele disse que era seu\Nconvidado, sabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:27.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E eu não achei que você\Nvoltaria tão cedo, Arlong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.52,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro, é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.48,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Which means, if I can just\Nbuy me a little more time... - OG}{Which means, if I can just buy myself a little more time... - Gaijin}{Then, I just need to buy\Nmyself a little more time... - arch}Então eu só preciso\Nganhar um pouco mais de tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.53,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que você fica se metendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.16,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo está tão perto de dar certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:46.83,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{So close! - OG}{I'm so close! - arch}Tão perto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{D-Damn you! You picking a fight?! - OG}{D-Damn you! You looking to fight?! - arch}D-Droga! Quer brigar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're getting in the way! - OG}{You're in the way! - Gord, CPS}Você está sendo um estorvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're the one to blame! - OG}A culpa é sua!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É isso que acontece\Nquando mexe com o Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami! You really disappoint me! - OG}Nami! Estou tão decepcionado com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:14.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo depois de roubar\Nnosso navio e fugir,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy didn't suspect you one bit! - OG}O Luffy não suspeitou de você por um segundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even now, he completely trusts you! - OG}Ele ainda confia totalmente em você!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How can you trick someone like\Nthat with such an uncaring look?! - OG}{How can you be so indifferent\Nabout tricking someone like that?! - arch}{How can you not care\Nabout tricking someone like that?! - Gord}Como você pode simplesmente\Nmentir na cara dele assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A única coisa em que eu confio é dinheiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Those who get fooled are the fools! - OG}{Those who get fooled deserve it! - arch}A ingenuidade dele é culpa dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Say what?! - OG}O que foi isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:34.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everything was supposed to go smoothly. - OG}{It was all supposed to\Ngo without a hitch. - arch}Era pra tudo ter dado\Ncerto sem problemas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:41.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You guys are going to make my\Neight years of business meaningless. - OG}Já que vocês estão tão ansiosos pra destruir\Nmeus oito anos de trabalho duro,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So the least I can do... - OG}eu é que deveria...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{is get rid of you by my own hand! - OG}ter o direito de matar vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:52.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Seems you've become a lot more\Npirate-like since you were last here! - OG}{It seems you're acting more like a\Npirate than before you left! - Gaijin}Você está agindo mais como pirata\Ndo que antes de sair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Get rid of? - OG}{Get rid of me? - Gaijin}{Put me down? - arch}Me matar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You, get rid of me?!\NDon't make me laugh! - OG}{You, off me?! Don't make me laugh! - arch}Você, me matar?!\NNão me faça rir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:04:59.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't underestimate me... - OG}Seria prudente...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{if I were you. - OG}não zombar de mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.49,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dammit... - OG}{Damn it. - Gaijin}Ah, droga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.87,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Se eu ficar aqui, estou morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Letal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Estrela de Fumaça!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bastard used a smoke bomb! - OG}O desgraçado usou uma bomba de fumaça!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Surround him! Don't let him escape! - OG}Cerquem ele! Não deixem escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora é minha chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:29.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is just like something you'd think up. - OG}{I thought you'd do something like this. - arch}Eu sabia que você\Nfaria algo assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's for my business! - 18:49 also AP07 @22:35}{It's just business! - Gord}Tenho um trabalho pra terminar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa era minha única opção!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{N-Nami, how could you...? - OG}{N-Nami, you just... - Z - this will make it a little more ambiguous}N-Nami, por que você...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Die like a good little boy. - OG}Agora seja bonzinho e morra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Muito bem, Nami!\N– Isso aí, se vingou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now that's why you're a\Nleader of the Arlong Pirates! - OG}{Now that's why you're an officer\Nof the Arlong Pirates! - Gaijin}É por isso que você é uma oficial\Ndos Piratas do Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:16.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{B-Big Sis Nami k-killed Big Bro Usopp! - OG}N-Não pode ser! A-A Mana Nami…!\NEla m-matou o Mano Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Era isso que você queria, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:22.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Morrer no mar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami, desculpa por duvidar de você.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're our friend. - OG}Você é uma de nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Friend? - OG}Uma de vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I have no friends! - OG}{I work for myself! - Gaijin}Eu trabalho sozinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:37.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's only one reason\Nwhy I joined this group! - OG}Só tem um motivo pelo qual\Neu entrei nessa tripulação!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra comprar a Vila Cocoyashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Keep your part of the bargain! - OG}Cumpra sua parte do acordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Logo terei os 100 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But of course. - OG}Claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:51.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'd rather cut my belly open and die than break a promise concerning money. - OG}Prefiro me matar do que\Nquebrar um acordo por dinheiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's the kind of man I am. - OG}Esse é o tipo de homem-peixe que eu sou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom saber, Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You know the score. - OG}Você sabe do acordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She's one creepy girl. - OG}{She's one creepy woman. - Gaijin}Aquela garota me dá arrepios.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What a truly great\Nwoman she's become! - OG}Ela realmente está se superando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A witch! - OG}Uma bruxa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She's really a witch! - OG}{She's actually a witch! - arch}Ela realmente é uma bruxa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ali está! Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Don't get tired, cow! - OG}Ei! Não desiste agora, vaca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:30.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É, os chutes do Mano Sanji\Ndevem ter feito um estrago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:34.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Não é pra lá!\NPra esquerda! Aquele prédio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que estamos voando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not "like"! - OG}Não "parece"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós estamos voando, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:05.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Estamos caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:19.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Landing successful! - OG}Aterrissamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yo! Zoro! - OG}Ei! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos! Conseguimos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Mas que droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{are you guys doing?! - OG}o que vocês idiotas estão fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:47.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como assim?\NViemos buscar a Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Have you still not found her? - OG}{You still haven't found her? - Gord}Ainda não encontrou ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, é. Onde estão\No Usopp e o Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:57.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Th-That's right! There's no time\Nto be loafing around here! - OG}I-Isso mesmo! Não temos tempo\Npra ficar de bobeira aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That bastard's been caught by Arlong! - OG}Aquele idiota foi pego pelo Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We gotta hurry before he's killed! - OG}Temos que correr antes que o matem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:04.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He was killed! - OG}É tarde demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Mano Usopp está morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He was killed! - OG}Ele foi assassinado!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pela Mana Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Depressa! Depressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual é a novidade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's the Marines! The Marines are here! - OG}A Marinha! A Marinha está aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:29.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alguns sobreviventes de Gosa\Nconseguiram contatar o governo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Marines have come\Nhere to pick us up! - OG}{The Marines have come to pick us up! - Gord}A Marinha veio nos resgatar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:34.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{See! - OG}Viram?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos salvos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:42.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We can finally escape this island! - OG}Finalmente podemos sair dessa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então esse é o infame Arlong Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:53.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The world's on its last legs if\Npirates can settle down so blatantly. - OG}Piratas se instalando tão descaradamente\Né sinal do fim dos tempos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Listen, men! - OG}Prestem atenção, homens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:10:01.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Our mission today is to successfully extract from the island... the survivors of the town of Gosa, - OG}Nossa missão hoje é libertar\Nos sobreviventes de Gosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{which was destroyed\Nby the Arlong Pirates! - OG}a cidade destruída\Npelos Piratas do Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But I am left to wonder... - OG}Mas não posso deixar de pensar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:11.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A nossa justiça nos permitiria\Nignorar o castelo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,desse pirata incontrolável?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– It would not!\N– It would not! - OG}– Não, senhor!\N– Não, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:20.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Our unit will now annihilate\NArlong and his men! - OG}Nossa unidade vai aniquilar\No Arlong e seus homens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para a batalha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:23.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Navy Branch #77? - OG}{The 77th Navy Branch? - Gaijin}A 77ª Divisão da Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes. That's what it said. - OG}Sim. Era o que dizia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:30.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A newcomer. - OG}Um rosto novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:32.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Someone go there and negotiate\Nwith the head honcho. - OG}{Someone go there and negotiate\Nwith the one in charge. - Gaijin}Alguém vá negociar\Ncom o responsável.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:36.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se dois milhões não forem o bastante\Npra impedi-los de fazer besteira,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{get rid of 'em! - OG}acabem com eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:43.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're suddenly opening fire! - OG}É um ataque surpresa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Arlong-san! Look out! - OG}Capitão Arlong! Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:58.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{H-He crunched a cannonball! - OG}{H-He pulverized that cannonball! - arch}E-Ele esmagou aquela bala de canhão!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What terrifying jaws and teeth! - OG}A mordida dele é aterrorizante!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Arlong-san. The negotiations? - OG}Capitão Arlong. As negociações?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:05.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Canceladas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:07.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right! Let's go! - OG}Beleza! Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:08.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hora de lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai ser um banho de sangue na Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Calma aí, galera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:21.20,Main-207-,,0,0,1,,{There's no need to expend so much\Nenergy just to take out the trash. - OG}{We don't need to waste so much\Neffort just to take out the trash. - arch}Não precisa mandar todo mundo\Nsó pra tirar o lixo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.91,Main-207-,,0,0,1,,{We'll go! - OG}Nós cuidamos disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:28.54,Main-207-,,0,0,1,,{What foolish humans they are to pick\Na fight with us in these waters. - OG}{These humans are damn fools to pick\Na fight with us in these waters. - arch}Esses humanos devem ser idiotas\Npor comprar briga conosco na água.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:32.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Three of our leaders'll\Nmake for a grand fight! - OG}{Three of our officers'll\Nmake for an epic fight! - arch}Três dos nossos oficiais?! Vai ser uma luta e tanto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:36.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That ship won't last\Neven three minutes! - OG}Aquele navio não dura três minutos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's odd... - OG}Que peculiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Commodore! The cannonball\Nappears to have been a dud! - OG}Comodoro!\NA bala de canhão não funcionou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Fire another! This is a signal of open hostility! - OG}Disparem outra! Precisamos\Ndemonstrar nossa intenção de lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're dealing with fishmen!\NDon't let your guard down, men! - OG}Estamos lidando com homens-peixe,\Nentão fiquem atentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele foi atingido!\NÉ um dos homens do Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Peguem ele! Iniciem o ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parem! Mantenham a calma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{One of Arlong's men, yes? - OG}Você é um dos homens do Arlong, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:04.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I am Commodore Purinpurin\Nof Navy Branch #77. - OG}Sou o Comodoro Pudding Pudding\Nda 77ª Divisão da Marinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:09.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We are a somewhat\Nwell-known elite Marine unit! - OG}Somos uma unidade de elite da Marinha\Nbem conhecida! Talvez tenha ouvido falar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:13.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you do not wish for death,\NI suggest you dutifully surrender– - OG}Se não deseja morrer,\Nsugiro que se renda obediente–
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Comodoro!\N– Comodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como ousa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Matem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What's this shock?! - OG}{Wh-What caused that impact?! - arch}Q-Que impacto foi esse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me there's\Nfishmen under the ship?! - OG}{\q2}Não pode ser...! Homens-peixe debaixo do navio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry to bother you like this, - OG}Desculpe incomodar assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:33.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but we just took the liberty\Nof removing your ship's rudder. - OG}mas tomamos a liberdade\Nde remover o leme do seu navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.44,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Comodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está tudo bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:41.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry.\NI didn't hit any vital spots. - OG}Não se preocupe. Não atingi\Nnenhum órgão vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é só hipotético,\NComodoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:50.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but if one were to move a large reef directly into a strong current, - OG}mas se alguém movesse uma rocha\Nenorme direto para uma corrente forte,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{what do you suppose would\Nhappen to the ocean? - OG}o que aconteceria com o oceano?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{M-Moving a reef?! - OG}{M-Moving rocks underwater?! - arch}Rearranjar o recife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That can't possibly be done! - OG}{That can't be possible! - arch}Isso é impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo! Mais ou menos ali, Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Right - OG}{Okay! - arch}Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Comodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A giant whirlpool has\Nsuddenly appeared ahead! - OG}Um redemoinho gigante acabou de se formar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O leme não funciona!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:11.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu avisei. Nós removemos o leme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse navio sem leme agora está indo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{into the depths of the sea. - OG}pro fundo do mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso não pode estar acontecendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa é a realidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tem como...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{we can escape from Arlong's control. - OG}escaparmos das garras do Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sorry to make you work so hard! - OG}Obrigado por isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not at all. We know everything about these waters, - OG}Não foi nada. Sabemos\Ntudo sobre essas águas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,dos ventos às profundezas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi moleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{With our top skills, we have no one to fear in these seas! - OG}{With our top-notch skills, no one\Nin these seas can challenge us! - arch}Com nossas habilidades de primeira,\Nninguém nesse mar pode nos desafiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E não vamos esquecer as cartas náuticas da Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Those are some excellent charts, all right! - OG}{Those are some damn\Ngood charts, all right! - arch}São umas cartas\Nincríveis, com certeza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:16.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If we have Nami draw up charts\Nof all the world's oceans, - OG}{we'll be the eternal kings of the sea! - OG}{\q2}Quando a Nami mapear todos os oceanos\Ndo mundo, seremos reis do mar para sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:22.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami's definitely vital to have for the creation of the Arlong Empire! - OG}{Nami's definitely vital in the creation\Nof the Arlong Empire! - arch}De fato, ela é a chave\Npra criar o Império Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:23.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É uma pena!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma pena?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He promised to let Nami\Nand Cocoyashi Village go - OG}Ele fez um acordo pra deixar a Nami\Ne a Vila Cocoyashi livres
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:30.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,assim que ela juntar 100 milhões de berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{For reals, Arlong-san?! - OG}{For real, Arlong?! - Gaijin}Está falando sério, Capitão Arlong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're really going to let Nami go?! - OG}Vai mesmo deixar a Nami ir embora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It can't be helped. - OG}Não tenho escolha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi o que concordamos\Noito anos atrás.
Comment: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:43.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm a man who'd die to keep\Nmy money-related promises. - OG}When it comes to money, I'd rather\Ndie than go back on my promises.{arch}
Comment: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,[Maybe split the line and put the next part here somehow?]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:45.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm a man who'd die to keep\Nmy money-related promises. - OG}{When it comes to money, I'd rather\Ndie than go back on my promises. - arch}Quando se trata de dinheiro,\Nprefiro morrer a voltar atrás.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Try saying that again!\NI'll kick your ass! - OG}Fala isso de novo e eu te arrebento!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:51.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para, Luffy. Isso não tem\Nnada a ver com o Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se não quer\Nacreditar em mim, não acredite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But I saw it with my own two eyes! - OG}Mas eu sei o que vi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela matou o Mano Usopp–
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Quit spouting nonsense! - OG}Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami would never kill Usopp! - OG}A Nami jamais mataria o Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're friends! - OG}Ela é uma de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas, eu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who're friends, Luffy? - OG}{Who's your friend, Luffy? - Gord}Uma de quem, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que vocês fazem aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What're you talking about? - OG}Como assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:17.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're our friend!\NWe came to get you! - OG}Você é uma de nós!\NViemos te buscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're a big problem. - OG}{You're such a nuisance. - Gord}Que saco.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Friends? - OG}Uma de vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:22.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me faça rir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're just a pathetic bunch of\Npeople cooperating with each other. - OG}{You're just a pathetic band\Nthat looks out for one another. - arch}Vocês mal funcionam como grupo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:27.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn you! You killed him! - OG}Sua bruxa! Você tem uma coragem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vi com meus próprios olhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:31.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como ousa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como ousa matar o Mano Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So what? - OG}{So what if I did? - PP}Grande coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why not kill me\Nas revenge, then? - OG}{Why not take your revenge\Nand kill me, then? - arch}Por que não me mata e\Nse vinga, então?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:38.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll tell you this much. - OG}Vou te dar um aviso.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:45.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora, o Arlong quer matar\NRoronoa Zoro e seus homens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Because Zoro just had to be stupid. - OG}O Zoro tinha que ir\Ne fazer besteira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:51.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter how monstrously\Nstrong you guys are, - OG}Não importa o quão monstruosamente\Nfortes vocês sejam,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,vocês não são páreo pra monstros de verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oi, Nami! Sou eu!\NVocê lembra de mim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos navegar juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, you!\NYou're just complicating things! - OG}Cala a boca!\NVocê só está complicando tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Say what?! - OG}Que isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O amor é sempre um furacão!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Listen when people are talking! - OG}Ei! Escuta quando alguém está falando!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:11.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cadê o Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bottom of the ocean. - OG}{On the ocean floor. - arch}No fundo do mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Para com essa palhaçada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:21.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A swordsman would even\Nstrike a lady, Roronoa Zoro? - OG}Então espadachins não se importam\Nem bater em mulheres, Roronoa Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:25.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Você nem sabe\No que está acontecendo aqui! Sai fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I guess I'd be irritated too,\Ncoming right off an insulting defeat. - OG}{I guess I'd be irritated too,\Ncoming right off a humiliating defeat. - arch}Acho que eu também ficaria irritado\Ndepois de levar uma surra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cuidado com essa sua boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:37.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Mind your own business,\Nyou damn bastard! - OG}Cuide da sua vida, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:41.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bros! This is no time\Nfor you two to be going at it! - OG}Manos! Não é hora\Npra vocês dois ficarem brigando!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you're going to fight,\Ncould you do it off the island?! - OG}Se vão brigar,\Npodem fazer isso fora da ilha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:48.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't butt any more into\Nthis land's affairs, you outsiders! - OG}Não se metam mais\Nnos nossos assuntos, forasteiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you still not get it? - OG}Ainda não entenderam, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:55.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A única razão pela qual eu\Nme aproximei de vocês foi pelo dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:59.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now that you're flat broke,\Nyou have no charm whatsoever! - OG}{Now that you're flat broke,\NI'm not interested whatsoever! - arch}Agora que vocês estão sem grana,\Nnão tenho o menor interesse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Podem ficar com o navio de volta,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so just go find a navigator\Nsomewhere and go into the Grand Line! - OG}{so go find another navigator\Nand go to the Grand Line! - Gaijin}então achem outro navegador\Npra levá-los até a Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vão procurar o\NOne Piece de vocês ou sei lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:10.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just get the hell out of here!\NYou're an eyesore! - OG}{Just get the hell away!\NYou're an eyesore! - Gord, CPS}Sumam daqui!\NEstou farta de ver vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Adeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mano Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to sleep. - OG}Hora de dormir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sleep?! - OG}Hora de dormir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In this situation?!\NAnd right in the middle of the road?! - OG}{At a time like this?!\NAnd right in the middle of the road?! - arch}Numa hora dessas?!\NNo meio da estrada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't plan on leaving the island, - OG}{I don't plan on leaving, - arch}Eu não vou a lugar nenhum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:36.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and I'm not interested in\Nwhat's happening on the island. - OG}{and I'm not interested in\Nwhat's happening here. - arch}e não estou interessado no\Nque acontece nessa ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And I'm a little sleepy. - OG}Só estou com um pouco de sono.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to sleep. - OG}Então vou tirar um cochilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:39.58,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tá...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Fine, whatever!\NGo ahead and die! - OG}Tá! Tanto faz! Morram, se quiserem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Na–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Mano Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What on earth are you thinking?! - OG}O que vocês estão pensando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Arlong quer nos matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So why aren't we running away?! - OG}Por que não estamos fugindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que sabemos como\Na Nami realmente é,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:09.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{there should be no reason\Nat all to stay on this island! - OG}não tem razão\Npra ficar nessa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A-All right! - OG}{A-Alright! - Gord}T-Tá bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:19.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi um reencontro curto,\Nmas nosso papel como guias termina aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:22.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Same for me! I don't wanna\Ndeliberately wind up killed! - OG}Concordo! Não quero\Nmorrer por causa disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se cuidem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom, até nos vermos de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stay well, you guys! - OG}Fiquem bem, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:31.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês também!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você realmente acredita que\Na Nami matou o Narigudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.83,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{When she did that! - OG}Naquela hora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.50,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's for my business! - OG}{05:41}Tenho um trabalho pra terminar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.96,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa era minha única opção!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.05,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{When she did that, - OG}Naquela hora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:15.76,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nami esfaqueou a própria mão\Npra parecer que me esfaqueou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:23.48,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{If Nami hadn't done that for me,\NArlong would've killed me for sure! - OG}Se não fosse a Nami,\No Arlong com certeza teria me matado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.48,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{What now?! - OG}O que eu faço?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:30.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Manly Usopp can't just turn\Ntail after being saved! - OG}O Viril Usopp não pode simplesmente\Nfugir depois de ser salvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.57,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Por enquanto, preciso achar o Zoro rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.70,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is that... Zoro?! - OG}Espera... É ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.41,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{It is! Yes! - OG}É sim! Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nami não matou ele.\NÉ isso que está tentando dizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou errado?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wonder. - OG}Quem sabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:50.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I did make her out to be a small fry\Nwho can't even watch a guy die. - OG}{I told her that she's just a little girl\Nwho can't even watch one guy die. - AP 01 - 25:38}Eu disse pra ela que era só uma garotinha\Nque não aguenta ver um cara morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She might've done it\Nout of frustration. - OG}Talvez isso tenha deixado ela irritada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Whadya mean, "small fry"?! - OG}{Whad'ya mean, "a lightweight"?! - arch}Como assim, "garotinha"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:56.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's so small about Nami-san's chest?! - OG}{What's so lightweight about Nami's chest?! - arch}O peito dela parece\Nde garotinha pra você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:57.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is that all you can think– - OG}Só pensa em–
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:04.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele está vivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:08.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\t(1857,0,1,\c&H070705&\3c&H070705&\4c&H070705&)}Não, acho que agora ele morreu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:29.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You really know how to trash a place. - OG}Você sabe como destruir um lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nada. Só vim descansar um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:41.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quebrar vidro e móveis\Nsó pra descansar é demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:47.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You have that treasure map open\Neven though nothing's wrong? - OG}Se não é nada, por que está\Nolhando fixo pra esse mapa do tesouro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We agreed you could tell me\Nanything, remember? - OG}Combinamos que você pode me\Ncontar qualquer coisa, lembra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Something happened to\Nmake me mad, that's all! - OG}Algo me irritou. Só isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Them, huh? Who are they? - OG}{It was them, huh? Who are they? - arch}Ah, eles. Quem são eles, afinal...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você encontrou eles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim. Capitão Alguma-Coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He seemed kind of liar-ish, though. - OG}Mas ele parecia ser um mentiroso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now I see... - OG}Agora entendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É, isso deve ter te abalado.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:22.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{To think that someone\Nreally showed up for her... - OG}{I'm surprised that someone\Nreally showed up for her. - arch}Estou surpresa que alguém\Nrealmente veio buscá-la.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:24.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Amigos, é...?
Comment: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:33.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please come up with a way to split this in three, it physically pains me to have a line like this - Gab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:28.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The most painful word for her... - OG}Essa palavra...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:30.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The most painful word for her... - OG}pra ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The most painful word for her... - OG}Nenhuma palavra poderia ser mais dolorosa...
Comment: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:33.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The most painful word for her...{Z - Maybe something like "That word..." "For her..." "no word could be more painful."}{Going with Z's for now, TLs can maybe improve}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:36.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:38.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nami fez isso com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sorry. Me and him did that. - OG}{Sorry. This guy and me did that. - Gaijin}{Sorry. Me and this guy did that. - arch}Desculpa. Fomos eu e esse cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Você conseguiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,L-Luffy! Você está aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Just got here. - OG}Sim. Acabamos de chegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:48.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I came, too!\NGood to work with you! - OG}{Oh, I'm here, too! Good to see you! - arch}Ah, eu também estou aqui! Que bom te ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:50.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um dia eu te mato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh! You're pretty alright after all! - OG}Opa! Você está bem\Nde saúde, afinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:53.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:57.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por falar nisso,\Nouvimos que a Nami te matou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:57.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Eh?! - OG}Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:01.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That damn Johnny! He was talking nonsense after all! - OG}{That damn Johnny! I knew it!\NHe was full of crap! - arch}Aquele maldito Johnny!\NEu sabia que estava mentindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:02.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:05.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In a way, it's not a lie... - OG}De certa forma, não era mentira.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:07.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But it's actually the opposite! - OG}Na verdade, é o contrário!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:10.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nami salvou minha vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:15.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It looks to me like there's a reason\Nshe's in a fishman pirate group! - OG}{It looks to me like there's a reason\Nshe's in a fishman crew! - arch}Deve ter algum motivo pra\Nela estar nessa tripulação de homens-peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:16.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Obviously. - OG}Com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E aí, o que fazemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:18.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Invadimos o Arlong Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Espera! Temos que descobrir\No que acontece com a Nami primeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:25.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's no use, either way. - OG}{Either way, it's no use. - Gord}De qualquer forma, é perda de tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:25.66,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:29.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter what you guys do,\NArlong's rule won't come to an end. - OG}Não importa o que vocês façam,\Nvocês não conseguem se livrar do Arlong.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:31.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem é ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:32.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A irmã mais velha da Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:36.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{N-Nami-san's older sister?!\NNo wonder she's so beautiful! - OG}A-A irmã mais velha da Nami?!\NCom razão ela é tão bonita!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean it's no use? - OG}Como assim "perda de tempo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please, don't get any more\Ninvolved with this village. - OG}Por favor, não se envolvam\Nmais com essa vila.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:44.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixem a Nami em paz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:46.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll explain the circumstances. - OG}Eu vou explicar o que está acontecendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'll feel like leaving\Nthe island once you hear it. - OG}Vocês vão querer sair\Nda ilha quando ouvirem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem um navio da Marinha na costa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:53.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's Branch #16's ship! - OG}É um navio da 16ª Divisão!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:56.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Talvez o quartel-general esteja agindo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:58.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{after what happened to Branch #77?! - OG}depois do que aconteceu\Ncom a 77ª Divisão!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I am Captain Nezumi of Marine Branch #16! - OG}Sou o Capitão Nezumi\Nda 16ª Divisão da Marinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:08.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bring me Genzo, the representative\Nof Cocoyashi Village! - OG}Tragam o Genzo, xerife\Nda Vila Cocoyashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:11.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sou o Genzo, Capitão.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:13.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É você, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Lead me to the house\Nof the girl named Nami. - OG}Me leve até a casa\Nda garota chamada Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:19.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami? But what on earth for?! - OG}Nami? Mas pra quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:25.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você só precisa mostrar o caminho.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=13}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=30}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
